<br>
Tak is a crit strike kinda smurf. I wanted to check out an envenom/dual wield rogue.<br>
<br>
Here's my data to date:<br>
Sephroth Ebonheart<br>
Lvl 11 Briton Infiltrator<br>
Slash 11<br>
Envenom 5<br>
Crit 7 (was drunk and accidentally trained crit on one night)<br>
Dual 1<br>
Ten points sitting around.<br>
<br>
Here are my questions:<br>
<br>
1. How good are dual wield styles for Albion? <br>
<br>
2. Do you dual wielders use the dual styles exclusively in PvE and/or RvR? <br>
<br>
3. How is the damage output? <br>
<br>
4. Anyone have a proven template?<br>
<br>
Thanks aforehand. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umayl.showPublicProfile?language=EN>mayl</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/1/02 10:04:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1997.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> .</span><hr size=1> I put like 2 points into dual wield and have not looked back.<br>
<br>
Granted only 21st level, but right now I have almost max stealth, crit strike and slash.  Rest into envenom.<br>
<br>
I can solo yellows fine (assuming something I don't have a penalty vs).<br>
<br>
The high slash evens out crit damage plus the slash styles seem to hit harder then anything in the dual wield spec line.<br>
<br>
Right now I open with BackstabII, Thigh cut and then use my two slash styles.  Maybe throw in hamstring when I get an evade.  <br>
<br>
Adding tons of points into dual wield does not seem profitable for me.  The slash styles are as good if not better.  The % increase is having the offhand weapon swing does improve.  However, I would rather have points into envenom instead where I can get more use and flexiablity then dual wield.<br>
<br>
I doubt I will put anymore points into dual wield.  <br>
<br>
The only disclaimer, is maybe thrust styles are poor and then dual wield specs make more since.. I have no idea as my main is a 42 cleric (so no weapon spec) and this guy is a slash infiltator. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse>The Safehouse</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19>Main Hall</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org">The Safehouse website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.guildboss.com"><img
